{"tid":1265442,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"東涌地盤墮15塊鋁板 壓斃工人","createTime":"2019-06-29T07:49:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-29T07:52:47.000Z","uid":142128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"8013ed4d2a92f1c269dc29e9a14d70b7c223ec39","tid":1265442,"uid":142128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T07:49:14.000Z","msg":"東涌迎禧路一個地盤，下午1時半左右，有鋁板在運送期間，由3米高位置墮下，壓住一名男工。傷者當場重傷昏迷，稍後由救護車送到北大嶼山醫院搶救，但告不治，警方及勞工處正展開調查。<br />\n<br />\n死者38歲姓蘇。警方調查後，相信死者搬運15塊，共約兩米乘兩米的鋁板時，被該批鋁板壓中，事件無可疑，列工業意外。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20190629/59770530\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190629%2F59770530&d=FYZ0PdCaIZeH%2BWUkJYSmqxZhTFX1FVJLw6RhI%2FCRHR8%3D&h=ffddd348\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190629%2F59770530&h=b8ca9921\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20190629/59770530</a><br />\n<br />\n又一單"},{"pid":"d2479960890cd6e44a5451756bf3c3b080483357","tid":1265442,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T07:52:47.000Z","msg":"lm"}]}